點色，啫係白底，尾巴、面加耳仔有黃色，因為顏色似焦糖燉蛋，所以咁叫<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"93f1531a4aea9d6b3875caf326610d4ebb638cde","tid":280551,"uid":19181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T18:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我隻貓叫燉蛋<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>希望唔好抄我<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n我有fd建議過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我養咗2兄弟，大佬叫焦糖，是黃貓，細佬叫燉蛋，紅重點色，啫係白底，尾巴、面加耳仔有黃色，因為顏色似焦糖燉蛋，所以咁叫<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n我就鐘意食蛋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ef8d68714ed08aad8229bdd28cdd5c3d5ae353","tid":280551,"uid":42598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T18:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我隻貓叫燉蛋<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>希望唔好抄我<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n我有fd建議過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我養咗2兄弟，大佬叫焦糖，是黃貓，細佬叫燉蛋，紅重點色，啫係白底，尾巴、面加耳仔有黃色，因為顏色似焦糖燉蛋，所以咁叫<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n我就鐘意食蛋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗咁多做咩，咩蛋都好，最尾都係會叫蛋蛋<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>既方便又快捷<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </sp